{{Infobox dungeon |name = Castelia Sewers |image = [[File:Castelia Sewers.png|300px]] |caption = A map of Castelia Sewers. |tokens = 146,500 |location = Castelia City }} '''Castelia Sewers''' is a [[Dungeons|dungeon]] in [[Unova]]. It initially has 81 tiles arranged in an 9x9 square, including 9 chest tiles, 21 non-boss encounter tiles, and 1 boss encounter tile.
